                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "gap": 24,
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "O8eKl",
                      "fill": "$color-text-1",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "为什么是图数据库",
                      "fontFamily": "$font-display",
                      "fontSize": 30,
                      "fontWeight": "700",
                      "letterSpacing": -0.5
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "HJZdK",
                      "fill": "$color-text-2",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "传统面试题库以 知识点 - 题目 的扁平结构存储,无法表达代码本身的拓扑关系。我们希望面试官能够 顺着调用栈追问,先看候选人对函数的实现,再追问该函数依赖的下游模块。这天然就是图。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.75,
                      "fontFamily": "$font-body",
                      "fontSize": 16,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "V4Ekn",
                      "fill": "$color-text-2",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "于是我们在 Neo4j 中建模了三类节点:Module、Function、Symbol;以及四类关系:CALLS、IMPORTS、DEFINES、SHADOWS。整个仓库的 AST 通过 tree-sitter 静态解析得到,落库时把每条边的位置信息(file: line) 也记下来,方便后续做引文式追问。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.75,
                      "fontFamily": "$font-body",
                      "fontSize": 16,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "r9QEBR",
                      "name": "Blockquote",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "fill": "$mesh-tint-1",
                      "cornerRadius": 8,
                      "gap": 16,
                      "padding": [
                        20,
                        24
                      ],
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "rectangle",
                          "id": "vl44S",
                          "fill": "$color-primary",
                          "width": 3,
                          "height": "fill_container"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "HDWco",
                          "fill": "$color-text-1",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "图不是结论,而是脚手架。模型最终回答的好坏取决于子图的剪枝策略,而不是图本身有多大。",
                          "lineHeight": 1.7,
                          "fontFamily": "$font-accent",
                          "fontSize": 16,
                          "fontWeight": "normal",
                          "fontStyle": "italic"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "uJfIv",
                      "fill": "$color-text-1",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "多智能体编排",
                      "fontFamily": "$font-display",
                      "fontSize": 30,
                      "fontWeight": "700",
                      "letterSpacing": -0.5
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "R2EuoC",
                      "fill": "$color-text-2",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "我们把 出题官、追问官、评分官 三个角色拆成三条提示词链:出题官读子图,生成 3 个候选题;追问官观察候选人的回答与执行结果,基于剩余子图选择追问路径;评分官接收完整对话历史,产出结构化评分。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.75,
                      "fontFamily": "$font-body",
                      "fontSize": 16,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
